/-- Nontriviality of the canonical Kummer bad-set character from the actual
locally-primary pseudo-unit hypotheses.

This combines the OSKR principal-vanishing corollary with the coprime
bad-set character construction and the Kummer splitting nontriviality engine.
The only reciprocity input is
`oneSidedKummerPrincipalReciprocity_canonical`, through
`locallyPrimaryPseudoUnit_principalSymbol_eq_zero_canonical_of_coprime_badSet`.
